    "description": "【游戏玩法】<br>游戏开始，玩家需要先学会操作方式，之后玩家需要找到没关的传送门通往下一个区域。<br>解开传送门谜题的方式包括摧毁机关，消灭怪物等<br>游戏中还有很多关闭的门，需要玩家在场景中找到钥匙进行解锁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074410/extras/e5e6c4a3a70ab501dfe08d3d877df316.poster.avif?t=1731289106\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074410/extras/e5e6c4a3a70ab501dfe08d3d877df316.webm?t=1731289106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074410/extras/e5e6c4a3a70ab501dfe08d3d877df316.mp4?t=1731289106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在《古道西风》中，玩家将扮演一名勇敢的探险者，踏上寻找失落文明的旅程。在这个充满未知的大陆上，古老的遗迹、神秘的森林、深邃的洞穴以及被遗忘的废墟，每一个角落都可能隐藏着危险或者宝藏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074410/extras/5b7535ee43353d2d5c19ad5c35c85074.poster.avif?t=1731289106\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074410/extras/5b7535ee43353d2d5c19ad5c35c85074.webm?t=1731289106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074410/extras/5b7535ee43353d2d5c19ad5c35c85074.mp4?t=1731289106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《古道西风》不仅仅是一款游戏，它是一次冒险，一次对未知世界的探索，一次心灵的旅程。加入我们，一起揭开古道西风背后的秘密。",
